      <title>棕榈油因印度需求强劲和林吉特疲软而延续涨势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/palm-oil-extends-gains-on-strong-indian-demand-and-weak-ringgit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[棕榈油价格连续第二天上涨，得益于全球最大买家印度的强劲需求，以及马来西亚货币走弱，使得这种热带油对海外买家更具吸引力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/palm-oil-extends-gains-on-strong-indian-demand-and-weak-ringgit</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 06:18:53 GMT</pubDate>
